Malena Cano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malena_Cano 0 Malena Cano (also known as La Perla) is a ranchero music and mariachi singer from the El Paso, Texas area. She is known for her work in both music and stage. Malena_Cano ( also_known as La_Perla ) is a_ranchero_music_and_mariachi_singer from the_El_Paso_,_Texas_area .
